text: Orania may refer to: * Orania (plant), a genus of palm trees * Orania (gastropod), a genus of molluscs * Orania Papazoglou, an American mystery writer * Orania, Northern Cape, an Afrikaner enclave in the Northern Cape, South Africa * FC Orania Vianden, a football club in Luxembourg * Orania (film), a 2012 film ==See also== * Oranje (disambiguation), a homophone of Orania Category:Genus disambiguation pages
